page.title: 20CONTRIBUTORS TO THE SURVEY.
page.content: The Survey of Witham has been undertaken jointly by Children from Witham Templars County Junior School and Witham Howbridge C.of E. (Controlled) Junior School during the Summer Term of 1985. The leaders were Mrs.Anne Mcdevitt at Witham Templars School and Mr. David Booth at Witham Howbridge Junior school. Contributions were compiled from Janet Gifford, Adam Dawkins, K.Rowe, P.Cole, K.Radley., T.Gibling, A.Lane, C.Worgan, and A.Poulter, N.Ferris, S.Comerasamy, G.U'ren, L. Walker, S.Rice, M. Agnew, S.Hull, A.Smart, G.Smith, R.Udoh .
